        "subject": "LU-11103 lod: add lock for lod_object layout",
        "message": "LU-11103 lod: add lock for lod_object layout\n\nlod_object layout is loaded on demand, and it may be updated\nby layout split/merge. To avoid race, add ldo_layouyt_mutex to\nserialize layout load/free/reload.\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/32589\nLustre-commit: I43c15a3b07254eadef95a14b288267904a1cd621\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Idb17850f4b4f716dc5b51147e7b3405739d0ce4c\n"
